# VER-016: Perspective Road Z-Test
# 
# Four-triangle road (2 quads) stretching into the distance.
# Tests Z interpolation and perspective depth gradient.
# 64x64 checker texture with 16x16 squares, bilinear filtered.
# Road split into 2 strips to keep V within Q4.12 range (max 4.0).
# Phase 'zclear': initialize Z-buffer to 0x0000 (reverse-Z far)
# Phase 'setup': configure texture and render mode
# Phase 'triangles': submit road strips (MVP-transformed)

## FRAMEBUFFER: 512 512
## TEXTURE: checker_wb base=0xC0000 format=RGB565 width_log2=6

## PHASE: zclear

# Clear color buffer: base_word=0x000000 value=0x0000 count=262144
44 0400_0000_0000_0000  # MEM_FILL: base_word=0x000000 value=0x0000 count=262144

44 0400_0000_0008_0000  # MEM_FILL: base_word=0x080000 value=0x0000 count=262144
40 0000_0099_0800_0000  # FB_CONFIG: color_base=0x0000 z_base=0x0800 w_log2=9 h_log2=9
43 0000_0080_2000_0000  # FB_CONTROL: scissor x=0 y=0 w=512 h=512

## PHASE: setup

# Upload 64x64 white/black checker (16x16 squares) texture at word 0xC0000
44 0010_00FF_FF0C_0000  # MEM_FILL: Fill 64x64 with 0xFFFF
44 0000_4000_000C_0040  # MEM_FILL: row 0 bx 4..7 (4 blk, 64 words)
44 0000_4000_000C_00C0  # MEM_FILL: row 0 bx 12..15 (4 blk, 64 words)
44 0000_4000_000C_0140  # MEM_FILL: row 1 bx 4..7 (4 blk, 64 words)
